Package: ShinyBasicAuth
Title: ShinyBasicAuth adds simple authentifcation to a shiny app, via a MySQL db
    table of users
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Tim", "Jones", email = "timothy.jones1@amey.co.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package adds authentication, and simple user management
    tools to Shinydashboard. It requires a MySQL database of users with user ids
    and hashed passwords. This package is still very much in development and lacks
    critical features such as the ability to add users.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.3)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    bcrypt (>= 0.2),
    data.table (>= 1.10.4),
    DBI (>= 0.5-1),
    magrittr (>= 1.5),
    shiny (>= 1.0.1),
    shinydashboard (>= 0.5.3),
    sodium (>= 1.1)
Suggests:
    pool (>= 0.1.0)
